Package org.team19

Class Fraction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.team19.Fraction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Fraction>
    public class Fraction
extends Object
implements Comparable<Fraction>
    Represents a rational number in the form of a simplified fraction

    This class does not account for long overflows
